    Low level area
    ============================================================================
    The ASM code of le32dec is:

    loc_80488DC:
    movzx   edx, byte ptr [ebx+3]
    movzx   eax, byte ptr [ebx+2]
    shl     eax, 10h
    shl     edx, 18h
    or      edx, eax
    movzx   eax, byte ptr [ebx+1]
    shl     eax, 8
    or      edx, eax
    movzx   eax, byte ptr [ebx]

    If [EBX], [EBX+2], [EBX+3] or [EBX+1] are a memory non readable the 
    application crashes.

